title: Ep 1922 - Iyer wants an Advice
shortDesc: Iyer is heart-broken and he is seen sharing his problems with friends. He is completely shattered and wants an advice to deal with the situation. However, Iyer thinks that Babita doesn’t love him anymore and he reveals that she was just compromisin

title: Ep 1923 - Jethalals Secret Meeting
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Jethalal discussing the problems of Iyer’s married life with Babita. Jethalal is trying to find out the root cause of the problem between the two without naming Iyer in his whole discussion with Babita.

title: Ep 1924 - Iyer Decides to Divorce Babita
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Iyer’s decision to give divorce to Babita; as he feels that Babita doesn’t love him and decides that it’s better to move out of the relationship. Moreover, he even thinks that Babita is feeling suffocated

title: Ep 1925 - Searching Girlfriend for Iyer
shortDesc: The secret meeting to discuss Iyer’s problem is interrupted by Babita. However, Jethalal and Bagha have managed the situation and luckily nothing is known to her. Later in the episode, we will get to know that Jethalal

title: Ep 1926 - Jethalals plan for Iyer
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Jethalal and his friends suggesting Iyer to carry out with the plans which they have devised by make Babita Jealous. However, the friends is suggesting Iyer to propose Sweety

title: Ep 1927 - Iyers Mission Affair
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with the execution of ‘Iyer’s Mission Affair’ in a shopping mall. He is with Sweety in a shopping mall where all the ladies of Gokuldham society will be arriving soon.

title: Ep 1928 - Iyers Affair Exposed
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Babita getting to know about Iyer’s extra-marital affair. She has seen Iyer and Sweety romancing in the shopping mall. Moreover, the ladies of the Gokuldham Society is trying to catch Iyer red handed

title: Ep 1929 - Iyer Hurts Babita
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with everyone assembling in Gokuldham Society compound to decide on Iyer’s fate. Champaklal is very angry with Iyer, after knowing about his affair with a girl.

title: Ep 1930 - Iyer wants Divorce
shortDesc: Champaklal is scolding Iyer for hurting Babita. He wants to know the address of the girl with whom Iyer is presently having an extra-marital affair. Iyer has completely denied giving any information about Sweety.

title: Ep 1931 - Sympathy for Iyer
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Iyer’s final decision to give a divorce to Babita; and for this Tarak informs Bhide to make the community hall available in the morning. As, the lawyer will be meeting the couple in the community hall

title: Ep 1932 - &amp;lsquo;C wing of Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with Bhide, Sodhi and Popatlal thinking about the outcome of the Iyer’s decision to divorce Babita. Everyone is very sad about the whole incident. It is then, Bhide thinks that something is wrong with the ‘C’ Wing .

title: Ep 1933 - Iyer decides to leave Gokuldham
shortDesc: Today’s episode revolves around Iyer and Babita’s final decision to divorce each other. The lawyer asks the couple to share their documents for filing joint divorce in the court. However, heartbroken Iyer comes out of the community hall

title: Ep 1934 - Iyer and Babita Saath Saath
shortDesc: Today’s episode continues with the residents of Gokuldham Society searching for Iyer and Babita. They want to make the couple make aware about their wrong decision which they have taken in haste.

title: Ep 1935 - Party in Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: Today’s episode revolves around Iyer and Babita’s problem getting solved. The misunderstanding between the two is now over and everyone in Gokuldham Society is very happy for them.

title: Ep 1936 - Mohammad Azharuddin Calls Popatlal
shortDesc: Former Indian Cricket Team captain Mohammad Azharuddin calls Popatlal to know about the Gokuldham Premiere League (GPL). He surprises Popatlal and his friends by calling them suddenly and he appreciates Jethalal
